description: The chefs at Mo’Rockin Fusion are bringing their extensive experience from cooking in Boston’s best restaurants, straight to the streets of Quincy. Everyone is just lovin’ their deliciously creamy hummus, juicy lemony chicken, fluffy and fragrant rice, and so much more. So come on out and rock your palate with the amazing mix of Mediterranean, Middle Eastern, and Moroccan cuisines that they’re cookin' up over at this marvelous truck!
name: Mo'Rockin Fusion
